{"tid":1492572,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"13拳肥仔認罪","createTime":"2019-08-21T01:35:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T06:09:49.000Z","uid":215260,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ec9f6416e9d9b4efcbcb3449d77988c9d1c12f0a","tid":1492572,"uid":215260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:36:00.000Z","msg":"入去坐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n46 歲的士司機黃堅海上周四（11日）凌晨企圖破壞位於淘大商場對出的九龍灣「連儂牆」，期間揮拳痛毆站在連儂牆前欲阻止他的男子，黃事後被控兩項襲擊致造成實際身體傷害罪。案件今早於官塘裁判法院提堂，被告戴著口罩抵庭，案件押後至下月底再訊，被告獲准保釋。<br />\n被告黃堅海報稱任職的士司機，案件押後至 8 月 30 日提訊，等待控方向律政司徵詢控罪意見。控方提到，被告在警誡下招認，現場有視像片段記錄案發經過。<br />\n裁判官溫紹明要求被告以 5,000 元現金繼續保釋，並於逢周一、三、五到警署報到，案件押後至 8 月 30 日提訊。<br />\n黃堅海被指在本月 11 日在九龍灣巴士站附近的「連儂牆」涉先後襲擊兩名看守的義工，包括連毆其中一名 36 歲義工 13 拳。<br />\n遇襲的 36 歲姓麥男子被拳打時，將雙手放在背後，不抵擋、沒有迴避，亦不還手。麥先生事後受訪指出，大學時曾習跆拳道並考獲黑帶，不還手是因為有學生和女士在場，擔心有任何動作都會激化事件，不想場面變混亂。"},{"pid":"8a7d2ecd40367ae8e8742c00934edc936b014859","tid":1492572,"uid":39215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:36:53.000Z","msg":"睇死坐幾日就出番黎"},{"pid":"07a8ec9abfd5a7db78233866b6daf965ca9b70fa","tid":1492572,"uid":6261,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:38:44.000Z","msg":"坐多過2年 我切"},{"pid":"564a2fd9fdc4e94eb46dea5f9f9802e25fea6dfd","tid":1492572,"uid":26106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07a8ec9abfd5a7db78233866b6daf965ca9b70fa","tid":1492572,"uid":6261,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:38:44.000Z","msg":"坐多過2年 我切"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:39:58.000Z","msg":"除時緩刑添呀"},{"pid":"40f0cd8b930944b094dd5b1453aabf5f40c89809","tid":1492572,"uid":245064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:40:03.000Z","msg":"一定判監<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過緩刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91e501616ea4450f3205714edb4d9885c64a0e81","tid":1492572,"uid":271267,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:42:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">呢啲仆街真係無資格做人,打個唔會還手既人,知唔知醜呀?</span></span>"},{"pid":"085bd74b480120ee8a397d5fafc931eba8939352","tid":1492572,"uid":215260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:44:40.000Z","msg":"襲擊致造成身體傷害<br />\n任何人因襲擊他人致造成身體傷害而被定罪，即屬犯可循公訴程序審訊的罪行，可處監禁3年。"},{"pid":"9cdf659070e059a66ddb98413b95f99916c947a8","tid":1492572,"uid":215260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91e501616ea4450f3205714edb4d9885c64a0e81","tid":1492572,"uid":271267,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:42:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">呢啲仆街真係無資格做人,打個唔會還手既人,知唔知醜呀?</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:45:14.000Z","msg":"仲要打個黑帶"},{"pid":"f26bf0e07282234cb90c834cfe36fca41c9bd986","tid":1492572,"uid":147367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:52:50.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，咁都用傷人39<br />\n13拳呀大佬"},{"pid":"16de26634427d3cdd7e46b26790a9aab327e4797","tid":1492572,"uid":209126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f26bf0e07282234cb90c834cfe36fca41c9bd986","tid":1492572,"uid":147367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:52:50.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，咁都用傷人39<br />\n13拳呀大佬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T02:06:38.000Z","msg":"我起初都以為會 wounding 19"},{"pid":"e61b9281717efb1e7b133800e1730bb6664d611a","tid":1492572,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T04:13:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1495238/page/1\" data-auto-link ta